    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this single-player roguelike, control an army of RECLAIMERS through a dangerous procedurally generated world. Explore, collect resources, and craft upgrades to advance your army to fight orcs, trolls, and more monsters. Defeat enemies in battle to collect better armor and weapons to finally fight the orc king.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crafting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With your RECLAIMERS, collect resources from the world to craft into weapons, tools and armor!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177010/extras/7606c833ad6c9542e32a301aa18ee37a.poster.avif?t=1744564181\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177010/extras/7606c833ad6c9542e32a301aa18ee37a.webm?t=1744564181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recruit RECLAIMERS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get more reclaimers for your army by finding houses with peasants in them. They want to reclaim the land just as much as you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177010/extras/5b065b875ead01908073efcd94597538.poster.avif?t=1744564181\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177010/extras/5b065b875ead01908073efcd94597538.webm?t=1744564181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Monsters:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Orcs normally reside in groups of 3 to 10 at their camps. They can be found in desert, snow and mountain biomes! They will throw a few punches but your RECLAIMERS can easily knock em down!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177010/extras/4a92d07661973a791d3a1a57d7e34a73.poster.avif?t=1744564181\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177010/extras/4a92d07661973a791d3a1a57d7e34a73.webm?t=1744564181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trolls are another foe who lurks in the mountain biome. They are far more dangerous and should be avoided at all costs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177010/extras/eb2d7b4729087804b8c6c1674eb0013e.poster.avif?t=1744564181\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177010/extras/eb2d7b4729087804b8c6c1674eb0013e.webm?t=1744564181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >List of Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore a procedurally generated open world full of dangerous monsters &amp; orcs! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Recruit members to your RECLAIMERS army from the several villages across the map. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive and fight back against orcs, trolls and other monsters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources from different biomes to craft tools, weapons and armor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack the Orc capital to face the Orc King and his legion of troops!</p></li></ul>",
